        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">Maintenance Support</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">
            For hostel administrative support, please contact <b>Respected Warden Sir 9031901500</b>
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">
