</div>

<div id="RuleModal"
     class="fixed inset-0 bg-black/40 hidden flex items-center justify-center">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 w-[450px] shadow-lg">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-center mb-4">Hostel Guidelines</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2">
            <li>Stay safe and avoid disputes with anyone.</li>
            <li>Study regularly and maintain discipline.</li>
            <li>Hostel entry time is 10:00 PM.</li>
            <li>Maintain cleanliness in your room and common areas.</li>
            <li>Respect hostel staff and fellow students.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="flex justify-center mt-6">
            <button id="RuleClose"
                    class="bg-primary text-white px-5 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary/90 transition">
                OK
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
